Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在与被称为悼词咏唱者的火焰之雾的激烈战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜得到了新的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜利然后分别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但当时的我却没能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜新的战斗快要逼近城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别追银了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个光追是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微留情点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己提出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是偶然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的 肯定不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,8)}{\bord2\1c&H3535FF&\3c&HCFCFCF&}恋爱和欲望的游泳池畔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热 真的好热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一大早就这么热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天热是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你现在懒得很啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算坚持每天早上的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却完全没有进步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也该考虑才能的成分嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 已经留好退路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想说的是 现阶段里 别用这种话来逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说起才能的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在能更好行动的基础上才谈的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再认真点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等一下啊 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了 池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了 池同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池 你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 因为父亲工作的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到大量御崎水上乐园的门票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就发给班上的同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御崎水上乐园就是那个最近才开张的「啊哈」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天啊 泳衣啊  御崎水上乐园  啊~~哈~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我想大家会不会很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是池
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  平井同学也有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  泳衣打算怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一副懒懒的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得拿到了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明后天就
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干  干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上课之前  对老师就有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领带太花哨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很新潮啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 悠二那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对着一张票傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游乐设施的入场券吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类很喜欢玩水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说来也很合乎情理了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样 心情和脸都太懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才没进步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 阿拉斯托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水上乐园是不是和浴室一样很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 去屋顶吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:06:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜还是没在中午前回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 平井同学去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邻镇的面包店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？为什么又
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可能中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然蜜瓜包重要的就是这种既香脆又松软的口感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  这个  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  不介意的话大家一起吃便当好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔这样也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人在一起边吃边开心地聊天比较有滋味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  便当总是吃便利店的饭团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  老妈说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男孩子如果一日三餐都吃母亲亲手做的饭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能出人投地了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的话不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是邀请坂井去水上乐园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 有事想商量下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得池同学的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天大家一起去水上乐园如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方同学  大家是指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 全班的话好像太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的人和那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边两人怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无所谓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阪井也没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井同学也没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班级里的女主角不来的话就不能开始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好是好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天10点在水上乐园集合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 你们可别迟到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩从以前开始就老是迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别随便决定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方 抱歉啊 有些事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像做了对不起绪方的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说周末无论如何都要把玛丘莉小姐 带到外面去的可是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天以来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐天天在房子里喝的烂醉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再不带她去哪玩玩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体就会坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这窝囊的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我烂醉的睡美人——玛丘莉·顿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  早上好  欢迎回来  又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件泳衣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也不那么花哨 这种挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪  绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都和男孩子一起去游泳池了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛穿老土的泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试穿这个之前衣服就交我保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱情爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 快穿快穿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再  再等会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好是好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方同学  你就饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是穿这个看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了普通的一件头就行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳衣给你买来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和大家一起去游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还穿学校的泳衣也太那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太那个了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说能穿上在学校不能穿的 可爱泳衣的意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就试穿看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里好好等着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道不知道学习这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了是误会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近有这个的话夏天可算是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中和佐藤好像真的不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话也一直没人接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩怎么都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们5个开心的玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水中情侣骑马战？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男女一组进行水中骑马战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优胜组的奖品是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到夜景的餐厅的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豪华晚餐免费招待券和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手制面包任吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手制面包任吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到夜景的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你的眼眸干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干  干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有意思的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正下午才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我参加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样决定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然少个男士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个等下再考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要着急不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是紫和一美的泳衣时装秀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是平井小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是吉田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪  绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 别管那么多 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐 别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不偶尔外出的话身体可会坏掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的情况出门反而对身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是这样也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荣太 那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丘莉小姐  真的要现在进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够避暑的只有这里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不如改明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的日子有些不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼词咏唱者来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？悼词的？那个人来这了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然感觉不到杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.09,0:15:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到两个火焰之雾都来这个游泳池悠闲地玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就有点想笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗嗦罗嗦罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去下小卖部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐一说出口就不听别人的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可能不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一碰到绪方她们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该说什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么多人在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能那么容易就碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你们俩在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:15:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是叫他们去买个酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启作和荣太都不知道在搞什么飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈 对你粗暴的喝酒方式终于忍受不了了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝了我的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊 喂 （发生了什么事吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道 虽然不太清楚  大概是三角关系之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  果然只是来玩的咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可没心情和你干架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想打的话找别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在水边喝点酒再睡一觉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼词咏唱者也就满足咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼词咏唱者作为火焰之雾也到头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但对我们来说无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  昨天说不去是为了吓大家一跳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想简单地说去太无趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 只是在这里突然出现热闹一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 田中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我也不告诉呢~~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话会参加骑马战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑马战？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带子连着的两人就组队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多出来的人就专心加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 大姐可是一直在等着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起玛丘莉小姐的事暴光来的要好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我放手咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御崎水上乐园特产
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水中情侣骑马战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规则很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抢到最多头巾的队伍就是优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 头巾被夺走或是两人分开就为失败
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池那家伙跑哪去上厕所了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说会好好加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在规定时间内抢到最多头巾的情侣将会得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看得到夜景的餐厅的晚餐和豪华奖品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和坂井同学在能看到夜景的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和坂井同学在能看到夜景的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了的话蜜瓜包任吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了的话蜜瓜包任吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗 田中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是靠你的机动力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 热闹激烈的水中骑马战开幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限定时间为3分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识的互相争夺也不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去抢别人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌~~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一美也挺不赖的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑马战果然还是要靠头脑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也有不靠头脑都很厉害的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 还要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井同学好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是佐藤比较厉害吧
